claim.claim-text:
1. An image forming apparatus comprising:
an image forming apparatus main body;
an image forming part provided in the image forming apparatus main body, to form an image on a recording medium;
an operation part configured to operate the image forming apparatus;
a support part provided on a bottom surface of the image forming apparatus main body and in contact with a mounting surface for the image forming apparatus main body to support the image forming apparatus main body; and
a convex part provided on the bottom surface,
wherein the convex part being provided on the operation part side from the support part, and is configured to form a clearance between the convex part and the mounting surface in response to no inclination of the image forming apparatus, and
wherein the convex part is configured to contact the mounting surface in response to inclination of the image forming apparatus.
